/www.thivien.net/T%E1%BB%AB-Huy%E1%BB%85n/author-PbzSOCmqBMTC0GXwXGPRrw">Từ Huyễn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BB%91ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%C3%ADn-Ch%C3%A2u-C%E1%BA%A7m-b%E1%BA%AFc-quy/poem-nCxYbCZrdCYm5RUxaSvBEg">Phụng tống Vương Tín Châu Cầm bắc quy - 奉送王信州崟北歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%C3%ADch-hoa/poem-OyPgnjg3EcvtCt6tBgYaXw">Tích hoa - 惜花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/Trung-thu-d%E1%BA%A1-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Quan-vi%C3%AAn-t%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A3nh/poem-AEC6I0cqYu-k5cNGd4tJCw">Trung thu dạ Đại Quan viên tức cảnh - 中秋夜大觀園即景</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br></div>	</div>
